ta" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_e7979fc8-b270-4635-8d0c-fe56db992e5a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Value</xref> of insulation.</li><li id="_73b7f2cf-0a63-4df9-8a69-8c684c4e2fcd">X = not permitted.</li><li id="_08c6b927-6d1c-4478-bcce-bda78369395b">This Table shows wall heights for single <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_f7f2bc81-c323-43c6-a7d4-d18d47a5d2ca" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">storey</xref> dwellings. For two <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1483_25.0.0.xml#_53ff3ea1-55e7-4f2a-b2b3-ca445ff64c15" id="_87ee684d-d648-46da-9a77-1d20a227b7a0" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">storey</xref> (or more) dwellings, add R0.5 to the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1420_0.4.0.xml#_e5acb40f-3d3d-4a3d-8987-f09f7eaadf77" id="_026b0325-b2d7-4c2c-8e72-afd15ab3f4be" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">R-Values</xref> given in this Table.</li><li id="_0303e278-c844-4a04-b07f-65500b3e9c44">Where an overhang of &gt; 600 mm is used, the values for &gt; 450 to ≤ 600 apply provided no more than 15% of the total opaque wall area of the dwelling (excluding windows/doors) is covered by overhangs &gt; 600 mm.</li></ol></desc-note></table-reference>